BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:all-upper-a@workout-calendar.rowlandpettit
DTSTAMP:20260607T155209Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260607T155209Z
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260608T070000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260608T080000
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY
SUMMARY:Lift: Upper A + Easy Run
DESCRIPTION:Stop at 8:00 even if unfinished.\n\n5 min warm-up:\n- Easy walk
  or bike\, shoulder circles\, band pull-aparts\, 10 push-ups.\n\n30 min l
 ift - Gym:\n- Bench press: 4 x 5-8.\n- Chest-supported row: 4 x 8.\n- Inc
 line DB press: 3 x 8-10.\n- Pull-ups or lat pulldown: 3 x 8-10.\n- Latera
 l raise + triceps pressdown: 2 x 12 each if time.\n\n30 min lift - Kettle
 bell:\n- Clean + press: 5 x 5 each side.\n- One-arm row: 4 x 8 each side.
 \n- Floor press: 4 x 10.\n- Push-up + suitcase carry: 3 rounds.\n\n30 min
  lift - No equipment:\n- Push-ups: 4 strong sets.\n- Pike push-ups: 3 x 8
 -12.\n- Prone swimmers: 3 x 12.\n- Chair dips: 3 x 10-15.\n- Plank: 3 x 4
 5 sec.\n\nAfter lift:\n- Easy treadmill run: 2 miles or 20 min cap\, whic
 hever comes first.\n\nMinimum version:\n- Warm-up\, bench/push-up\, row/p
 ull\, 10 min easy jog.
LOCATION:Gym or home
CATEGORIES:FITNESS,LIFTING,UPPER
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:all-lower-a@workout-calendar.rowlandpettit
DTSTAMP:20260607T155209Z
