SEQUENCE:0
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260609T070000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260609T080000
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY
SUMMARY:Lift: Lower A + Low-Impact Finish
DESCRIPTION:Stop at 8:00 even if unfinished. No hard running after lower bo
 dy.\n\n5 min warm-up:\n- Easy bike or walk\, hip circles\, bodyweight squ
 ats\, glute bridges.\n\n30 min lift - Gym:\n- Back squat: 4 x 5.\n- Roman
 ian deadlift: 3 x 8.\n- Reverse lunge: 3 x 8 each leg.\n- Calf raise + pl
 ank: 2-3 rounds.\n\n30 min lift - Kettlebell:\n- Goblet squat: 4 x 10.\n-
  Kettlebell swing: 5 x 15.\n- Split squat: 3 x 8 each leg.\n- Suitcase de
 adlift: 3 x 10.\n- Calf raise + side plank: 2 rounds.\n\n30 min lift - No
  equipment:\n- Split squat: 4 x 10 each leg.\n- Single-leg RDL reach: 3 x
  10 each leg.\n- Glute bridge: 4 x 15.\n- Wall sit: 3 x 45 sec.\n- Calf r
 aise + dead bug: 3 rounds.\n\nFinish:\n- Pick one easy option for 8-12 mi
 n: incline walk\, bike\, row\, sled\, carries\, or very light jump rope t
 echnique.\n\nMinimum version:\n- Warm-up\, squat pattern\, hinge pattern\
 , core.
LOCATION:Gym or home
CATEGORIES:FITNESS,LIFTING,LOWER
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:all-wednesday-choice@workout-calendar.rowlandpettit
DTSTAMP:20260607T155209Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260607T155209Z
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260610T070000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260610T080000
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY
SUMMARY:Choice: Swim 20 or Glory Muscles
DESCRIPTION:Wednesday is a choice day. Keep it useful\, not crushing.\nStop
  at 8:00 even if unfinished.\n\nOption A - Swim 20:\n- 4 x 50 easy warm-u
 p.\n- 4 x 50 drill: catch-up\, fingertip drag\, kick\, choice.\n- 6 x 100
  smooth\, 20 sec rest.\n- 4 x 25 build\, easy back.\n\nOption B - Glory M
 uscles - Gym:\n- DB curl + rope pressdown: 3 x 10-12 each.\n- Lateral rai
 se + rear delt fly: 3 x 12 each.\n- Hanging knee raise or cable crunch: 3
  x 10-15.\n- Standing calf raise: 4 x 12.\n- 5 min mobility.\n\nOption B 
 - Kettlebell:\n- Curl variation or towel curl: 3 x 12.\n- Close-grip push
 -up: 3 x 10-15.\n- Halo: 3 x 8 each way.\n- Suitcase carry: 4 short walks
 .\n- Calf raise + hollow hold: 3 rounds.\n\nOption B - No equipment:\n- D
 iamond push-ups: 3 strong sets.\n- Pike push-ups: 3 x 8-12.\n- Towel curl
 s: 3 x 12.\n- Hollow hold + calf raise: 4 rounds.\n- Mobility: 5 min.\n\n
 Minimum version:\n- 20 min easy swim\, walk\, mobility\, or core.
LOCATION:Pool\, gym\, or home
CATEGORIES:FITNESS,CHOICE,SWIM,ACCESSORIES
END:VEVENT
