SUMMARY:Lift: Upper B + Easy Run
DESCRIPTION:Stop at 8:00 even if unfinished.\n\n5 min warm-up:\n- Easy walk
  or bike\, shoulder circles\, scap push-ups\, light rows.\n\n30 min lift 
 - Gym:\n- Overhead press: 4 x 5-8.\n- Pull-ups or lat pulldown: 4 x 6-10.
 \n- DB bench press: 3 x 10.\n- Seated cable row: 3 x 10.\n- Rear delt rai
 se + hammer curl: 2 x 12 each if time.\n\n30 min lift - Kettlebell:\n- St
 rict press: 5 x 5 each side.\n- Renegade row or one-arm row: 4 x 8 each s
 ide.\n- Push-up: 4 strong sets.\n- High pull: 3 x 10 each side.\n- Farmer
  carry: 3 short walks.\n\n30 min lift - No equipment:\n- Pike push-ups: 4
  x 8-12.\n- Push-ups: 4 strong sets.\n- Doorframe/isometric row or prone 
 row: 4 x 12.\n- Rear delt snow angels: 3 x 12.\n- Side plank: 3 x 30 sec 
 each.\n\nAfter lift:\n- Easy treadmill run: 2 miles or 20 min cap\, which
 ever comes first.\n\nMinimum version:\n- Warm-up\, press\, pull\, 10 min 
 easy jog.
