SUMMARY:Lift: Lower B + Low-Impact Finish
DESCRIPTION:Stop at 8:00 even if unfinished. No hard running after lower bo
 dy.\n\n5 min warm-up:\n- Easy bike or walk\, hamstring sweeps\, hip airpl
 anes\, bodyweight lunges.\n\n30 min lift - Gym:\n- Deadlift or trap bar d
 eadlift: 4 x 3-5.\n- Front squat or leg press: 3 x 8.\n- Hamstring curl: 
 3 x 10.\n- Bulgarian split squat: 2 x 8 each leg.\n- Calf raise + dead bu
 g: 2 rounds if time.\n\n30 min lift - Kettlebell:\n- Double or single KB 
 deadlift: 4 x 8.\n- Front-rack squat: 4 x 8.\n- Swing: 5 x 12.\n- Reverse
  lunge: 3 x 8 each leg.\n- Suitcase carry: 3 short walks.\n\n30 min lift 
 - No equipment:\n- Single-leg glute bridge: 4 x 10 each leg.\n- Walking l
 unge: 4 x 12 each leg.\n- Hamstring walkout: 3 x 8.\n- Squat tempo reps: 
 3 x 15.\n- Calf raise + plank: 3 rounds.\n\nFinish:\n- Pick one easy opti
 on for 8-12 min: incline walk\, bike\, row\, sled\, carries\, or mobility
 .\n\nMinimum version:\n- Warm-up\, hinge pattern\, lunge pattern\, core.
